title: "Beyond the Smile: A Hybrid Convolutional VAE for Crypto Volatility Surfaces"
abstract: >-
  Reproduction code and processed data for a convolutional variational
  autoencoder with a deterministic hybrid reconstruction rule, trained on
  crypto options implied-volatility surfaces.
